            <q>the additional amounts paid into child trust funds under section 12".</q>
            On the first day in Grand Committee we debated the question of varying the way in which the charge cap might operate to enable child trust funds to be marketed more efficiently and effectively than might otherwise be the case. An annual report on the lines proposed in the amendment would provide the means to cast an investigative light on how the additional payments are working.
